         <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="verticalLayout_info">
          <item>
           <widget class="QLabel" name="label_description">
            <property name="text">
             <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;authlib-injector is a Java agent that allows Minecraft to use custom Yggdrasil authentication servers (such as LittleSkin or custom skin servers).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It is automatically downloaded when you launch a game with a Yggdrasil account, but you can also manage it here.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For more information, visit &lt;a href=&quot;https://authlib-injector.yushi.moe/&quot;&gt;authlib-injector.yushi.moe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
